---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Verkada Video Security Cameras | Blue Cap IT — Gold Partner" description="Blue Cap IT sells and installs Verkada AI-powered security cameras. Cloud-managed, no NVR required. Official Verkada Gold Partner. Call (410) 858-4031.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="verkada.html">Verkada Solutions</a> <span>/</span> Video Security Cameras</div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Verkada Solution</div>
          <h1>Video Security <span class="grad">Cameras</span></h1>
          <p class="section-sub">AI-powered, cloud-managed cameras with built-in storage and zero on-site servers. See everything, from anywhere, on any device.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Camera Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost btn-sm">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/Cameras_Family_Portrait_Pillars.png" alt="Verkada Security Cameras" class="feature-img"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 4rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Why Verkada Cameras</div>
        <h2>Smarter Cameras.<br/><span class="grad">Zero Complexity.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0.8rem auto 0;">Verkada cameras combine on-board AI processing with cloud management to deliver enterprise-grade surveillance without the enterprise-grade headaches.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">🧠</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>On-Board AI Analytics</h3>
            <p>Each Verkada camera processes AI analytics locally — no separate servers required. Get real-time intelligence built into every device.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Person &amp; vehicle detection with instant alerts</li>
              <li>License plate recognition (LPR) on compatible models</li>
              <li>Facial recognition &amp; watchlist alerts</li>
              <li>Crowd detection and occupancy monitoring</li>
              <li>Motion search — find footage in seconds</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">☁️</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>True Cloud Management</h3>
            <p>Every camera is managed through Verkada Command — a browser-based dashboard accessible from anywhere. No VPN, no NVR, no on-premise server.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Live view and playback from any browser or mobile app</li>
              <li>Automatic firmware updates pushed by Verkada</li>
              <li>Multi-site management from one unified dashboard</li>
              <li>Granular user permissions and audit logs</li>
              <li>10-year hardware warranty on all cameras</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">💾</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Hybrid On-Board Storage</h3>
            <p>Video footage is stored directly on the camera's built-in solid-state drive — up to 365 days of local storage — and backed up to the cloud simultaneously.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>No NVR or DVR required — ever</li>
              <li>Up to 365 days of on-board video retention</li>
              <li>Automatic cloud backup included</li>
              <li>Footage survives network outages</li>
              <li>Tamper-evident encrypted storage</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="specs-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Camera Lines</div>
      <h2>Verkada Camera <span class="grad">Models</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT carries the full Verkada camera lineup. Contact us for pricing and availability.</p>
      <div class="specs-grid">
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/cameras/mini-dome.jpg" alt="Indoor Mini Dome Camera" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>Indoor Dome (D-Series)</h4><ul><li>4MP, 5MP, 8MP options</li><li>Ceiling or wall mount</li><li>Wide dynamic range</li><li>Built-in microphone</li><li>Ideal for offices &amp; retail</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/cameras/outdoor-dome.png" alt="Outdoor Dome Camera" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>Outdoor Dome (CD-Series)</h4><ul><li>IP66 weatherproof rating</li><li>IK10 vandal resistant</li><li>4K ultra-HD available</li><li>Built-in IR night vision</li><li>Ideal for entrances &amp; parking</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/cameras/ptz-camera.png" alt="PTZ Camera" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>PTZ Cameras</h4><ul><li>Pan / Tilt / Zoom control</li><li>32x optical zoom</li><li>Auto-tracking</li><li>Wide area coverage</li><li>Ideal for large open areas</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><h4>🚗 License Plate (LPR)</h4><ul><li>Dedicated LPR processing</li><li>Reads plates at speed</li><li>Searchable plate database</li><li>Watchlist &amp; alert triggers</li><li>Ideal for parking &amp; gates</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/cameras/bullet-camera.png" alt="Bullet Camera for Low Light" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>Low-Light Cameras</h4><ul><li>Color imaging in near-darkness</li><li>No IR glare or halo</li><li>F1.0 aperture available</li><li>Superior night performance</li><li>Ideal for lobbies &amp; hallways</li></ul></div>
        <div class="spec-card"><img src="/verkada/cameras/fisheye-camera.png" alt="Fisheye 360° Camera" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;" /><h4>Fisheye 360°</h4><ul><li>Full 360° panoramic view</li><li>Replaces multiple cameras</li><li>Dewarped live playback</li><li>12MP sensor</li><li>Ideal for open floor plans</li></ul></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <div class="section-label">Watch</div>
      <h2>Verkada Cameras <span class="grad">in Action</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;">See how Verkada's AI-powered cameras deliver smarter security with cloud management, built-in storage, and real-time analytics.</p>
      <div style="position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;height:0;overflow:hidden;border-radius:1rem;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5oIER0pcyEk" title="Verkada Video Security Cameras" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1.5rem 4rem;">
      <div class="section-label">Resources</div>
      <h2>Verkada Camera <span class="grad">Downloads</span></h2>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;margin-top:2rem;">
        <a href="/verkada/docs/ai-powered-search-alerts-overview.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-ghost" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">📄 AI-Powered Search & Alerts Overview</a>
        <a href="/verkada/docs/traditional-vs-ai-powered-investigations.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-ghost" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">📄 Traditional vs AI-Powered Investigations</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Ready to See a Demo?</div>
    <h2>Let Blue Cap IT Design Your<br/><span class="grad">Camera System</span></h2>
    <p>We'll assess your site, recommend the right Verkada camera models, and provide a detailed quote — completely free.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Request a Free Site Assessment</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
